              },
              "free_text": [
                " A STACK OF NINE 50",
                " MG/CM2 THICK AU FOILS, COVERED ON BOTH SIDES WITH 1 MM",
                " THICK CADMIUM SHEETS, WAS USED FOR NEUTRON FLUX DETER-",
                " MINATION. BY STUDYING THE ACTIVITIES THROUGH THE",
                " FOILS, CORRECTIONS FOR THE EPITHERMAL NEUTRONS COULD",
                " BE APPLIED."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".TO ABTAIN A SIZABLE 3-HE TARGET DENSITY, AN ALUMINIUM",
                " TARGET GAS CELL, 10.2 CM LONG, 3.0 CM IN DIAMETER AND",
                " WITH 0.3 CM THICK WALLS, WAS KEPT AT A TEMPERATURE OF",
                " 11.8 +/- 0.4 K AND A PRESSURE OF 23.0 +/- 0.4 BARS.",
                " THIS RESULTED IN A 3-HE DENSITY OF 1.48 +/- 0.05 TIMES",
                " E+22 NUCLEI/CM3."
              ]
            }
          ],
